id: mbedtls_sha
package: platform
label: SHA Function Families
description: >-
  This component provides support for all SHA hash functions supported by
  Silicon Labs in Mbed TLS. This includes SHA-1, SHA-224, SHA-256, SHA-384,
  and SHA-512.
category: Platform|Security|Mbed TLS|Hashing
quality: production
# Seems like a rare use case. Users can still require all other components.
ui_hints:
  visibility: never
provides:
  - name: mbedtls_sha
requires:
  - name: mbedtls_sha1
  - name: mbedtls_sha256
  - name: mbedtls_sha512
metadata:
  sbom:
    license: Apache-2.0
    upstream:
      name: Mbed TLS
      version: v3.6.2
      supplier: Trusted Firmware
      url: https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls.git
      comment: Mbed TLS is a C library implementing the PSA Cryptography API, cryptographic primitives, X.509 certificate manipulation and the SSL/TLS and DTLS protocols
